definitions.definition: A mass of oat plants (genus Avena , especially Avena sativa ).
examples: Oats are in the north corner of the farm.
Usually oats is last in a rotation and does not get the fertilizer that other feed grains get.

definitions.definition: Seeds of an oat plant, especially prepared as food.
examples: Oats is a heart-healthy breakfast food.
